00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.000 line:80% position:20% align:start
On this page, you can see the posts
from all the users you follow.

00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:10.000 line:80% position:20% align:start
To have them appear here, first visit a
user's profile and click "Follow".

00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:15.000 line:80% position:20% align:start
Once followed, their messages are
grouped in this dedicated section.

00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:20.000 line:80% position:20% align:start
You can access this personalized feed
via the star icon in the menu.